text:
Nia Imani Franklin (born July 27, 1993) is an American beauty pageant winner and Miss America 2019.
Born in Winston-Salem, North Carolina, Franklin moved to New York City in 2017.
In June 2018, she was crowned Miss New York 2018. On September 9, 2018, she was crowned [https://viralbigo.com/miss-america-2019-has-been-announced-know-who-has-been-crowned-this-year/ Miss America 2019] in Atlantic City, New Jersey. For the talent portion she sang "Quando m'en vo''" from the opera, "La bohème".
